       <div>

         <div class="w-full h-60 mb-28 flex">
            <div class="relative top-10 left-10 z-10 bg-neutral-700 text-white py-4 px-6 rounded h-[70%] w-full flex flex-col gap-3">
               <h4 class="text-2xl tracking-wide">Personal Storyboards</h4>
               <p class="text-sm ">Here are some of my personal Storyboards, some of them are exercises from college, ando others like Stranger are personal projects.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="w-[180%] relative -left-20">
               <img class="object-contain h-full w-full" src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/a9013c_b9060ba4e405472288aa20acae06a838~mv2.png/v1/fill/w_479,h_241,al_c,q_85,usm_0.66_1.00_0.01,enc_avif,quality_auto/a9013c_b9060ba4e405472288aa20acae06a838~mv2.png" alt="">
